'''[[滿地可銀行|BMO]]球場'''（{{lang-en|BMO Field}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]][[多倫多|多倫多]]一座戶外體育場，現為[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美國職業足球大聯盟]]（MLS）[[多倫多FC|多倫多FC]]、[[加拿大加式足球聯盟|加拿大加式足球聯盟]]（CFL）[[多倫多淘金人|多倫多淘金人]]及[[美國足球聯賽|美國足球聯賽]]多倫多FC II的主場館。場館坐落[[加拿大博覽會|加拿大博覽會]]會場，業權由多倫多市政府擁有，營運權則歸{{link-en|楓葉體育及娛樂有限公司|Maple Leaf Sports & Entertainment}}。球場2007年4月28日首次啟用，第一場賽事為多倫多FC對[[堪薩斯城巫師|堪薩斯城巫師]]，結果主隊以0:1敗陣。

此場館原為一座{{link-en|足球專用體育場|Soccer-specific stadium}}，供2007年起作賽的多倫多FC使用，而[[2007年國際足協U-20世界盃|2007年國際足協U-20世界盃]]和[[2014年國際足協女子U-20世界盃|2014年國際足協女子U-20世界盃]]部分賽事（包括前者的開幕賽和決賽）亦在此進行。場館亦於2010年、2016年和2017年三度舉辦[[美國職業足球大聯盟盃|美國職業足球大聯盟盃]]決賽，當中主隊多倫多FC於2017年贏取獎盃。場館亦曾於[[2015年泛美運動會|2015年泛美運動會]]期間舉辦[[七人欖球|七人欖球]]賽事，而[[加拿大國家橄欖球隊|加拿大國家橄欖球隊]]亦曾在此進行主場賽事。場館從2014-16年間進行重修，在東看台新設上層觀眾席，在觀眾席上方增添屋頂，並延長草坪以迎合[[加拿大式足球|加拿大式足球]]賽事。工程完成後，淘金人隊從2016年CFL賽季起以此作其主場館。

球場在舉辦國際賽時會稱為「國家足球場」（{{lang|en|National Soccer Stadium}}）。

==歷史==

BMO球場是展覽館內同一位置上所興建的第五座球場，之前一座名為{{link-en|會展體育場|Exhibition Stadium}}，是[[加拿大加式足球聯盟|加拿大加式足球聯盟]]（CFL）[[多倫多淘金人|多倫多淘金人]]及和[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]][[多倫多藍鳥|多倫多藍鳥]]的主場館。但自天虹體育館（2005年起改稱[[羅渣士中心|羅渣士中心]]）於1989年落成後，該場館便失去長期租戶，因此在1999年拆卸。

淘金人隊雖於羅渣士中心作賽，但該場館的設計偏重棒球，因此該隊曾於2001年向多倫多市政府申請重修蘭波特體育場（{{lang|en|Lamport Stadium}}）並將之擴張至可容納19000名觀眾<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/argos-u-of-t-look-at-lamport/article25448094/|title=Argos, U of T look at Lamport|date=2001-04-12|accessdate=2018-06-03|newspaper=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215150140/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/argos-u-of-t-look-at-lamport/article25448094/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；到了2003年3月建議則改為在[[加拿大博覽會|加拿大博覽會]]會場新建一座可容納22000人的體育場<ref name=2005council/>。另一方面，為了競逐[[2007年國際足協U-20世界盃|2007年國際足協U-20世界盃]]主辦權，[[加拿大足球協會|加拿大足協]]於同年7月宣布斥資8200萬加元在該處興建一座體育場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.canadasoccer.com/csa-releases-details-on-proposed-national-soccer-stadium-p147569|title=CSA Releases Details On Proposed National Soccer Stadium|date=July 21, 2003|accessdate=February 27, 2015|publisher=[[加拿大足球協會|加拿大足球協會]]|archive-date=2018-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823110125/https://www.canadasoccer.com/csa-releases-details-on-proposed-national-soccer-stadium-p147569|dead-url=no}}</ref>，若成功申辦賽事的話加拿大聯邦政府和安大略省政府將為項目提供合共3500萬元撥款<ref name=varsity/>。此外，[[國家冰球聯盟|國家冰球聯盟]][[多倫多楓葉|多倫多楓葉]]和[[NBA|NBA]][[多倫多速龍|多倫多速龍]]的母公司{{link-en|楓葉體育及娛樂有限公司|Maple Leaf Sports & Entertainment}}當時正考慮向[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美國職業足球大聯盟]]（MLS）申辦一支多倫多足球隊，並希望在市内設立一座{{link-en|足球專用體育場|Soccer-specific stadium}}。

淘金人隊、加拿大足協和楓葉體娛遂於2004年5月宣布合資8千萬元在[[多倫多大學|多倫多大學]]的市中心校園興建一座可容納25000人的體育場<ref name=varsity>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/football/new-stadium-for-argos-canadian-soccer-1.511637|title=New stadium for Argos, Canadian soccer|date=May 21, 2004|accessdate=January 8, 2014|publisher=CBC News|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815094947/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/football/new-stadium-for-argos-canadian-soccer-1.511637|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=brick/><ref name=sun>{{cite web|url=http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Football/CFL/Toronto/2004/10/01/651476.html|title=Sun sets on Varsity|date=October 1, 2004|accessdate=January 8, 2014|work=Toronto Sun|last=Lefko|first=Perry}}</ref>。除了來自兩級政府的撥款外，多大亦為項目注資1500萬元，並將成為球場的東主<ref name=varsity/>。然而，楓葉體娛其後因項目回報欠佳而退出，而隨着項目造價上漲逾1億元，多大新任校長履新後亦退出項目，球場遂未能成事<ref name=brick>{{cite web|url=http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Football/CFL/Toronto/2004/11/04/700446.html|title=Brick by brick|date=November 4, 2004|accessdate=January 7, 2014|publisher=Toronto Sun|last=Lefko|first=Perry}}</ref><ref name=sun/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/football/plan-for-toronto-football-stadium-crumbles-1.486858|title=Plan for Toronto football stadium crumbles|date=September 30, 2004|accessdate=January 8, 2014|publisher=CBC News|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815094952/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/football/plan-for-toronto-football-stadium-crumbles-1.486858|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

淘金人隊和加拿大足協其後改為建議在[[約克大學_(加拿大)|約克大學]]校園興建球場，預算造價為7千萬加元，當中2千萬元來自淘金人隊，1500萬元來自約大，土地亦由校方提供<ref name=brick/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yorku.ca/yfile/archive/index.asp?Article=3464|title=A new stadium for York|date=October 19, 2004|accessdate=January 8, 2014|publisher=[[約克大學_(加拿大)|約克大學]]|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108081228/http://www.yorku.ca/yfile/archive/index.asp?Article=3464|dead-url=no}}</ref>；楓葉體娛並未參與此項目<ref>{{cite news|title=Ex feels jilted by Argos; City's phone calls to CFL team go unanswered Sources say club to announce York as its new home|date=October 14, 2004|last=Byers|first=Jim|publisher=[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]}}</ref>。然而羅渣士中心卻同意為淘金人隊減租，雙方遂達成協議繼續租約，新球場項目亦告吹<ref>{{cite web|url=http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Football/CFL/Toronto/2005/05/03/1023523.html|title=Argos run a reverse|date=May 3, 2005|accessdate=January 8, 2014|last=Koreen|first=Mike|publisher=Toronto Sun}}</ref>。

加拿大足協繼續與楓葉體娛磋商，雙方終在2005年同意在加拿大博覽會會場内的加拿大體壇名人堂所在興建球場，預算造價為6290萬加元<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/February2011/23/c5131.html|title=BMO Field, MLSE delivers financial return to City of Toronto|accessdate=February 23, 2011|archive-date=2011-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110226231242/http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/February2011/23/c5131.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。加拿大聯邦政府為項目提供2700萬元，安省政府提供8百萬元，多倫多市政府則提供980萬元並成為球場的東主<ref name=approved>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/toronto-city-council-approves-soccer-stadium-deal-1.536727|title=Toronto city council approves soccer stadium deal|date=October 27, 2005|accessdate=October 1, 2013|publisher=CBC News|archive-date=2016-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160812165951/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/toronto-city-council-approves-soccer-stadium-deal-1.536727|dead-url=no}}</ref>。楓葉體娛提供8百萬元，項目超支的話亦由該公司負責<ref name=approved/>，藉此換取球場的營運權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://slam.canoe.ca/Slam/Soccer/TorontoFC/2009/06/03/pf-9660301.html|title=Grass at BMO remains a contentious issue|date=June 3, 2009|last=Sandor|first=Steven|publisher=Toronto Sun}}</ref>。多倫多市政府通過的項目協議中列明球場將可改建以迎合加式足球規格<ref name=2005council>{{cite web|url=http://www.toronto.ca/legdocs/2005/agendas/council/cc051026/pof9rpt/cl036.pdf|title=Soccer Stadium at Exhibition Place|publisher=City of Toronto|accessdate=January 8, 2014|date=October 2005|archive-date=2019-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117020027/https://www.toronto.ca/legdocs/2005/agendas/council/cc051026/pof9rpt/cl036.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bmobuilt>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/bmo-built-with-football-in-mind/article4222875/|title=BMO built with football in mind|date=August 13, 2008|accessdate=January 8, 2014|publisher=The Globe and Mail|last=Naylor|first=David|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215150141/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/bmo-built-with-football-in-mind/article4222875/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而淘金人隊亦曾於最後階段希望參與項目，但楓葉體娛期望項目以原定時限和預算完成，球場因此按原定設計興建。球場若改建以迎合加式足球規格的話，底線區一帶的看台需拆卸重建<ref name=bmobuilt/><ref name=dreamjob>{{cite book|title=Dream Job|last=Peddie|first=Richard|year=2013|publisher=[[HarperCollins|HarperCollins]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/brunt-no-room-for-argos-at-new-soccer-stadium/article1111476/|title=No room for Argos at new soccer stadium|last=Brunt|first=Stephen|newspaper=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|date=December 7, 2006|accessdate=May 17, 2014|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215150140/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/brunt-no-room-for-argos-at-new-soccer-stadium/article1111476/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2006年5月11日，[[美國職業足球大聯盟|美國職業足球大聯盟]]（MLS）宣布多倫多FC將於2007年成為聯盟的第十三支球隊（加拿大首隊）。MLS專員{{link-en|唐·加伯|Don Garber}}稱新加盟球隊須有興建足球專用球場計劃，並指由於此類球場面積相對[[國家美式足球聯盟|國家美式足球聯盟]]或者[[加拿大加式足球聯盟|加拿大式足球聯賽]]球場較小，有助觀眾營造更佳氣氛，而且球隊對有關設施有較大自主權，更能有效控制收入與成本。

同年8月31日，《[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]》報道[[滿地可銀行|-{zh-hans:蒙特利尔银行; zh-hk:滿地可銀行}-]]購得球場的命名權。（購入前球場只稱作國家足球場。）“BMO”是-{zh-hans:蒙特利尔银行; zh-hk:滿地可銀行}-的簡稱，亦是該行在[[多倫多證券交易所|多倫多證券交易所]]上的股票代號，{{pronEng|ˈbiːmoʊ}}。儘管銀行以「[[蒙特利尔|-{zh-hans:蒙特利尔; zh-hk:滿地可}-]]」命名，總部其實設在多倫多。9月20日，球場西看台懸掛印有 "BMO Field" 字樣的旗幟，後來在多倫多FC的網站正式宣布球場易名的消息。儘管如此，球場舉行在[[國際足協|國際足協]]認可比賽時，依然稱作「國家足球場」。

2007年5月12日，球場開幕。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://toronto.fc.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20061204&content_id=79841&vkey=news_t280&fext=.jsp&team=t280|title=Toronto FC to kick off inaugural season in California|date=12/04/2006|publisher=Toronto FC Media Relations|accessdate=2009-11-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208152838/http://toronto.fc.mlsnet.com/news/team_news.jsp?ymd=20061204&content_id=79841&vkey=news_t280&fext=.jsp&team=t280|archivedate=2009-02-08}}</ref>開幕禮上，MLS專員宣布「2008年MLS明星賽」({{link-en|MLS All-Star 2008|MLS All-Star 2008}}) 及2012年「MLS盃」將在這裡舉行。

自2009年春季起，[[美國職業袋棍球大聯盟|美國職業袋棍球大聯盟]]（MLL）球隊多倫多國家隊（{{lang|en|Toronto Nationals}}）在BMO球場進行聯賽主場賽事。該隊於翌年賽季遷至蘭波特體育場，2011年遷至[[哈密爾頓_(安大略省)|哈密爾頓]]，2013年則告解散。

2009年11月，媒體報道[[多倫多淘金人|多倫多淘金人]]正與多倫多市政府商討從[[羅渣士中心|羅渣士中心]]遷至BMO球場，最快於2010年CFL賽季落實<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/football/argos-to-leave-rogers-centre/article1379458/|title=Argos to leave Rogers Centre?|date=November 26, 2009|accessdate=December 2, 2009|location=Toronto|newspaper=The Globe and Mail|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20091130150743/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/football/argos-to-leave-rogers-centre/article1379458/|archivedate=2009-11-30|deadurl=no}}</ref>。場館的長度較正式加式足球賽場所需為短，CFL需研究淘金人隊在此作賽是否可行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/football/story/2009/11/28/sp-argos-bmo.html|title=CFL to study new venue for Argos|accessdate=December 2, 2009|work=CBC News|date=November 28, 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091202235634/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/football/story/2009/11/28/sp-argos-bmo.html|archivedate=2009-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。CFL最終結論為BMO球場以當前狀況不適舉行加式足球賽事，淘金人隊遂於同年12月16日宣布放棄遷址<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.argonauts.ca/article/statement-regarding-cfl-feasibility-study-on-bmo-field|title=Statement Regarding CFL Feasibility Study on BMO Field|accessdate=December 16, 2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091220152722/http://www.argonauts.ca/article/statement-regarding-cfl-feasibility-study-on-bmo-field|archivedate=2009-12-20|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

雷維克（{{lang|en|Tim Leiweke}}）於2013年接任楓葉體娛總裁，其後談及該公司計劃為BMO球場進行大型改修<ref name=shoalts>{{cite news|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/football/leiweke-outlines-mlse-plans-for-stadium-renovation/article16570810/|title=MLSE outlines plans for stadium renovation, with eye on NFL team|date=January 29, 2014|accessdate=February 2, 2014|publisher=The Globe and Mail|last=Shoalts|first=David|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215150140/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/sports/football/leiweke-outlines-mlse-plans-for-stadium-renovation/article16570810/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/mlse-looking-at-100m-roof-for-bmo-field-1.1872030|title=MLSE looking at $100M roof for BMO Field|date=September 28, 2013|accessdate=October 1, 2013|publisher=CBC News|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215150141/https://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/mlse-looking-at-100m-roof-for-bmo-field-1.1872030|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=paidback>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2014/01/19/mlses_leiweke_taxpayers_would_be_paid_back_for_bmo_field_expansion.html|title=MLSE's Leiweke: Taxpayers would be paid back for BMO Field expansion|first=Daniel|last=Dale|date=January 19, 2014|accessdate=|publisher=Toronto Star|archive-date=2018-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907110242/https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2014/01/19/mlses_leiweke_taxpayers_would_be_paid_back_for_bmo_field_expansion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；他於2014年1月表示將於往後半年與專家研究項目可行性<ref name=soothes>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/soccer/toronto-fc-bmo-field-argos-tim-leiweke-cfl-mls/|title=Leiweke soothes TFC fan worries over BMO expansion|date=January 9, 2014|accessdate=January 12, 2014|last=Molinaro|first=John|publisher=Sportsnet|archive-date=2018-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907221328/https://www.sportsnet.ca/soccer/toronto-fc-bmo-field-argos-tim-leiweke-cfl-mls/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於球場東主為多倫多市政府，楓葉體娛進行項目前需獲取市府同意<ref name=endorsed>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2014/03/19/bmo_field_upgrade_endorsed.html|title=BMO Field upgrade endorsed|date=March 19, 2014|accessdate=March 19, 2014|newspaper=Toronto Star|last=Moloney|first=Paul|archive-date=2018-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180623222019/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2014/03/19/bmo_field_upgrade_endorsed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨着淘金人隊與羅渣士中心的租約於2017年賽季後屆滿，市府堅持改修項目需包括將賽場增長以容納加式足球賽事<ref name=citypushing>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2014/03/07/mlse_city_pushing_to_move_argos_to_bmo_field.html|title=MLSE: City pushing to move Argos to BMO Field|date=March 7, 2014|accessdate=March 8, 2014|newspaper=Toronto Star|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113170304/http://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2014/03/07/mlse_city_pushing_to_move_argos_to_bmo_field.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=excomrep>{{cite web|url=http://www.toronto.ca/legdocs/mmis/2014/ex/bgrd/backgroundfile-67466.pdf|title=Renovation and Expansion of BMO Field|date=March 5, 2014|accessdate=March 15, 2014|publisher=City of Toronto|archive-date=2019-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208044354/https://www.toronto.ca/legdocs/mmis/2014/ex/bgrd/backgroundfile-67466.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=makeover>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2014/03/14/mlse_wants_10_million_from_toronto_for_bmo_field_makeover.html|title=MLSE wants $10 million from Toronto for BMO Field makeover|date=March 14, 2014|accessdate=March 16, 2014|newspaper=Toronto Star|last=Tepper|first=Sean|archive-date=2016-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113170304/http://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2014/03/14/mlse_wants_10_million_from_toronto_for_bmo_field_makeover.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=bigbucks>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2014/03/16/mlse-plans-to-spend-big-bucks-to-upgrade-bmo-field|title=MLSE plans to spend big bucks to upgrade BMO Field|last=Larson|first=Kurtis|date=March 16, 2014|accessdate=March 16, 2014|newspaper=Toronto Sun|archive-date=2017-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170804053538/http://www.torontosun.com/2014/03/16/mlse-plans-to-spend-big-bucks-to-upgrade-bmo-field|dead-url=no}}</ref>。副市長凱利（{{lang|en|Norm Kelly}}）表示淘金人隊「需在此作賽」，並認為成事機會頗高<ref name=kelly>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2014/03/14/norm-kelly-wants-city-to-advance-mlse-10-million-for-bmo-improvements|title=Norm Kelly wants city to advance MLSE $10 million for BMO improvements|last=Peat|first=Dan|newspaper=Toronto Sun|date=March 14, 2014|accessdate=March 16, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002019/http://www.torontosun.com/2014/03/14/norm-kelly-wants-city-to-advance-mlse-10-million-for-bmo-improvements|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

場館改建項目初步方案於2014年3月公布<ref name=plans>{{cite web |url=http://www.explace.on.ca/database/rte/files/2014_0305%20BMO%20Field%20-%20Public%20Meeting_FINAL.pdf |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309031754/http://www.explace.on.ca/database/rte/files/2014_0305%20BMO%20Field%20-%20Public%20Meeting_FINAL.pdf |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2014-03-09 |title=BMO Field – Public Meeting |date=March 5, 2014 |accessdate=March 8, 2014 |publisher=Maple Leaf Sports & Entertainment }}</ref><ref name=futurebmo>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2014/03/05/is-this-the-future-of-bmo-field|title=Is this the future of BMO Field?|date=March 6, 2014|accessdate=March 8, 2014|newspaper=Toronto Sun|last=Larson|first=Kurtis|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915045833/http://www.torontosun.com/2014/03/05/is-this-the-future-of-bmo-field|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨了改建賽場以容納加式足球賽事外，項目亦包括在場館東側增設上層看台。足球賽事的觀眾席數遂從21566席增至30000席，加式足球觀眾席數為26500席，而舉行大型賽事和活動時底線區亦可增設臨時觀眾席，達致最高容量4萬人<ref name=citypushing/><ref name=excomrep/><ref name=makeover/><ref name=bigbucks/><ref name=plans/><ref name=loi>{{cite web|url=http://www.toronto.ca/legdocs/mmis/2014/ex/bgrd/backgroundfile-67468.pdf|title=Proposal for Expansion of Stadium at Exhibition Place|date=March 10, 2014|accessdate=March 15, 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304044433/http://www.toronto.ca/legdocs/mmis/2014/ex/bgrd/backgroundfile-67468.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sportsnet.ca/hockey/24-7/winter-classic-could-be-coming-to-toronto/|title=Toronto could host Winter Classic in 2017|date=December 31, 2013|accessdate=January 3, 2014|publisher=Sportsnet|archive-date=2018-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180907150015/https://www.sportsnet.ca/hockey/24-7/winter-classic-could-be-coming-to-toronto/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。改建項目分兩期進行，首期包括增長賽場和增建觀眾席，耗資7700萬元，2015年5月完成。次期則包括在永久觀眾席上方增添屋頂，耗資4300萬元，2016年5月完成<ref name=endorsed/><ref name=excomrep/><ref name=bigbucks/><ref name=loi/>。

楓葉體娛其中兩名主要股東[[加拿大貝爾|加拿大貝爾]]和基爾默集團（{{lang|en|Kilmer Group}}）於2015年5月20日宣布購入淘金人隊部分股權，並計劃從2016年CFL賽季起將該隊主場置於BMO球場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://argonauts.ca/article/bell-canada-and-kilmer-group-to-acquire-argonauts|title=Bell Canada and Kilmer Group to acquire Argonauts|publisher=Toronto Argonauts|date=May 20, 2015|accessdate=May 20, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522130512/http://argonauts.ca/article/bell-canada-and-kilmer-group-to-acquire-argonauts|archivedate=2015-05-22}}</ref>。協議包括在改建完畢的BMO球場舉行兩次[[格雷杯|格雷杯]]賽事<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2015/04/24/argos-fate-rests-on-talks-with-mystery-group.html|title=Argos' fate rests on talks with mystery group|date=April 23, 2015|accessdate=April 23, 2015|first=Jennifer|last=Pagliaro|newspaper=Toronto Star|archive-date=2018-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901113213/https://www.thestar.com/news/city_hall/2015/04/24/argos-fate-rests-on-talks-with-mystery-group.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontosun.com/2015/04/24/live-leiweke-updates-bmo-field-argos-talks|title=New owner could help Argos land new home|date=April 23, 2015|accessdate=April 23, 2015|first=Jenny|last=Yuen|newspaper=Toronto Sun|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075050/http://www.torontosun.com/2015/04/24/live-leiweke-updates-bmo-field-argos-talks|dead-url=no}}</ref>。場館於2016年2月宣布與[[滿地可銀行|-{zh-hans:蒙特利尔银行; zh-hk:滿地可銀行}-]]的命名權協議續期十年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.torontofc.ca/post/2016/02/22/bmo-and-mlse-announce-10-year-naming-rights-renewal-bmo-field|title=BMO and MLSE Announce 10-Year Naming Rights Renewal For BMO Field|date=2016-02-22|accessdate=2016-02-22|publisher=Toronto FC|archive-date=2016-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225061424/http://www.torontofc.ca/post/2016/02/22/bmo-and-mlse-announce-10-year-naming-rights-renewal-bmo-field|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===其他歷史事件===

*2007年9月7日，球場舉行目前為止唯一一場音樂會，演出者為古典搖滾樂隊[[創世紀樂團|創世紀樂團]]。
